    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Main halls, or "golden halls," of Buddhist temples or sanctuaries; used particularly for some early Buddhist temples into the 8th century. For the main halls of temples in general, use hondō.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
